HEADWORD: Hermaphroditism
<hw>Her*maph"ro*dit*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>The union of the two sexes in the same
individual, or the combination of some of their characteristics or
organs in one individual.</def></p>

